### Get all analysis results
GET http://localhost:7071/api/results

### Get a specific analysis result (replace the ID with an actual one)
GET http://localhost:7071/api/results/58571e1c-4aa7-4085-a14e-968ee7837791

### Get results with a limit (last 5)
GET http://localhost:7071/api/results?limit=5

### Get results for a specific blob (if you implement this endpoint)
# GET http://localhost:7071/api/results?blobName=test_image.png

### Check if the function app is running (health check)
GET http://localhost:7071/api/results
HTTP/1.1 200 OK

### Alternative: Get full analysis details
# GET http://localhost:7071/api/results/{id?}

### Test production endpoint (replace with your Azure URL when deployed)
# GET https://yourname-image-analyzer.azurewebsites.net/api/results
